{"id":233349,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/06/维权网-重庆访民戴月权在京被抓后遭殴打拘留劳/","date":"2012-06-20T09:16:00Z","modified":"2012-06-20T09:16:00Z","title":"维权网 | 重庆访民戴月权在京被抓后遭殴打拘留劳教（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'> </a>（维权网信息员关小令报道）本网信息员获悉，家住重庆市铜梁县的残疾访民戴月权，被铜梁县副县长陈友国带人前往北京将其抓回当地关押一个月后，又转为劳动教养一年零三个月，只是口头告知，不给劳教手续。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span> </p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据知情人说，戴月权是于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>，在他租住地北京市丰台区吕村的公路上，被铜梁县副县长陈友国带人跟踪抓捕，跟踪人将毫无防备的戴月权用头套套住头部后，迅速戴上手铐，并对其进行殴打。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>访民戴月权被抓捕押送回重庆市铜梁县后，铜梁县公安局于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span><span>给其家属送达一份拘留通知书，告知戴月权涉嫌聚众扰乱社会秩序刑事拘留，被羁押铜梁县看守所。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>，访民戴月权被送进重庆市北碚区西山坪劳教所九大队执行一年零三个月的劳教期，但政府不给劳教手续。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日</span><span>，戴月权的妻子廖保翠前往劳教所见到戴月权，返回到家后，政府官员开着几辆车来找她，使她倍感身处险境，不愿向外吐露更多信息，只是说见到戴后，戴告诉说抓他时遭到殴打，送劳教所后身体很差，强迫训练。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>访民戴月权是因修水库时受工伤，政府每月只给</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">35</span><span>元工资，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>元医药费，使他无法生活，被迫上访后，遭政府拘留，关黑监狱等迫害。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-55ERwirW-_4/T-F6z0YxPGI/AAAAAAAAInE/GD_aqwcU5DQ/s1600/%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E6%88%B4%E6%9C%88%E6%9D%83.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-55ERwirW-_4/T-F6z0YxPGI/AAAAAAAAInE/GD_aqwcU5DQ/s320/%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E6%88%B4%E6%9C%88%E6%9D%83.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-bbJdJVj6FXc/T-F62UxSaWI/AAAAAAAAInM/uXgQGZ3GdUY/s1600/%E6%88%B4.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-bbJdJVj6FXc/T-F62UxSaWI/AAAAAAAAInM/uXgQGZ3GdUY/s320/%E6%88%B4.jpg\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-2845556433473871536?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/7a4c187788E69D83.JPG-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[9085,16910,19196]}